#: index.docbook:64
msgid "The <application>ht://dig</application> Programs"
msgstr "Programy <application>ht://dig</application>"

#: index.docbook:66
msgid ""
"There are three programs KDE needs that come with <application>ht://dig</"
"application>: <command>htdig</command>, <command>htsearch</command> and "
"<command>htmerge</command>. For each program you have to provide the full "
"path including the program name, for example: <filename class=\"directory\">/"
"usr/bin/htdig</filename>."
msgstr ""
"KDE potrebuje tri programy, ktoré sú súčasťou <application>ht://dig</"
"application>: <command>htdig</command>, <command>htsearch</command> a "
"<command>htmerge</command>. Pre každý z nich musíte zadať úplnú cestu spolu "
"s menom programu, napríklad: <filename class=\"directory\">/usr/bin/htdig</"
"filename>."

#: index.docbook:72
msgid ""
"Where exactly these programs are installed depends on your operating system "
"or your distribution. However, there are some good guesses you might want to "
"try:"
msgstr ""
"To, kde sú tieto programy presne nainštalované, závisí od vášho operačného "
"systému alebo distribúcie. Toto sú ale obvyklé hodnoty, ktoré môžete "
"vyskúšať:"

#: index.docbook:76
msgid ""
"<command>htdig</command> and <command>htmerge</command> are often found in "
"<filename class=\"directory\">/usr/bin/</filename> or in something like "
"<filename class=\"directory\">/usr/local/www/htdig/bin/</filename>."
msgstr ""
"<command>htdig</command> a <command>htmerge</command> sú často v priečinku "
"<filename class=\"directory\">/usr/bin/</filename> alebo niekde ako "
"<filename class=\"directory\">/usr/local/www/htdig/bin/</filename>."

#: index.docbook:76
msgid ""
"the <command>htsearch</command> command is often found in a sub directory "
"called <filename class=\"directory\">cgi-bin</filename>, for example "
"<filename class=\"directory\">/usr/local/httpd/cgi-bin/</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Príkaz <command>htsearch</command> je často v podpriečinku <filename class="
"\"directory\">cgi-bin</filename>, napríklad <filename class=\"directory\">/"
"usr/local/httpd/cgi-bin/</filename>."

#: index.docbook:90
msgid ""
"To find out where for example <command>htdig</command> is installed you can "
"always type <command>whereis htdig</command> on the console. "
"<command>whereis</command> will look for the specified command in the "
"standard execution path directories. However, directories like <filename "
"class=\"directory\">cgi-bin</filename> are often not in the standard "
"execution path."
msgstr ""
"Umiestnenie napríklad programu <command>htdig</command> môžete zistiť "
"príkazom <command>whereis htdig</command> z konzole. Príkaz "
"<command>whereis</command> nájde zadaný príkaz v štandardných priečinkoch "
"pre spustiteľné súbory. Uvedomte si ale, že priečinky ako <filename class="
"\"directory\">cgi-bin</filename> sa obvykle za štandarné nepovažujú."

#: index.docbook:100
msgid "Scope and Search Paths"
msgstr "Rozsah a cesty pre hľadanie"

#: index.docbook:102
msgid ""
"In this section you can choose which help resources should be indexed, "
"<abbrev>i.e.</abbrev> made available to the search engine."
msgstr ""
"V tejto časti môžete vybrať, ktoré zdroje sa majú spracovať a dať k "
"dispozícii vyhľadávaciemu stroju."

#: index.docbook:105
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Scope</guilabel> frame you can select some typical "
"resources you want to be indexed, <abbrev>i.e.</abbrev> the KDE help files, "
"and the information offered by the <command>man</command> and <command>info</"
"command> commands. Note that some of those may still be disabled, which "
"means that support for them has not been added yet."
msgstr ""
"Rámec <guilabel>Rozsah</guilabel> umožňuje vybrať typické zdroje, ktoré sa "
"majú indexovať, napr. KDE pomocník a informácie poskytované príkazmi "
"<abbrev>man</abbrev> a <command>info</command>. Niektoré z nich ale môžu byť "
"neprístupné, pretože pre ne chýba momentálne podpora."

#: index.docbook:111
msgid ""
"Maybe you have additional files you want to access using the KDE Help "
"Center's fulltext search feature. For example, you might have an "
"<abbrev>HTML</abbrev> reference installed in <filename>/home/jdoe/docs/"
"selfhtml</filename>. By adding this path to the list of additional search "
"paths you make this documentation available to KDE Help Center's fulltext "
"search, too. Just click on the <guibutton>Add</guibutton> button and a file "
"dialog will ask you for an additional search directory. Select <filename>/"
"home/jdoe/docs/selfhtml</filename> and click <guibutton>OK</guibutton>. To "
"remove an additional search path, just select it and click "
"<guibutton>Delete</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Možno máte nejaké ďalšie súbory, ktoré chcete mať prístupné pomocou "
"vyhľadávania v Pomocníkovi KDE. Napríklad chcete dokumentáciu k jazyku "
"<abbrev>HTML</abbrev>, ktorá je napr. v priečinku <filename>/home/jdoe/docs/"
"selfhtml</filename>. Pridaním tejto cesty dáte túto dokumentáciu k "
"dispozícii v hľadaní v KDE Pomocníkovi. Cestu pridáte pomocou tlačidla "
"<guibutton>Pridať</guibutton> a zobrazí sa dialóg pre zadanie novej cesty. "
"Vyberte teda <filename>/home/jdoe/docs/selfhtml</filename>. a stlačte "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton>. Cestu odstránite jednoducho výberom zo zoznamu a "
"stlačením tlačidla <guibutton>Odstrániť</guibutton>."

#: index.docbook:122
msgid ""
"Your changes to the scope and additional search paths will not take effect "
"if you don't click on the <guibutton>Generate index ...</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Ak zmeníte rozsah a cesty, tieto zmeny sa neprejavia skôr, než použijete "
"tlačidlo <guibutton>Vytvoriť index...</guibutton>."

#: index.docbook:129
msgid "Selecting the language"
msgstr "Výber jazyka"

#: index.docbook:130
msgid ""
"You can select the language you want the help files in using the combo box "
"labeled <guilabel>Language Settings</guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"Môžete si aj nastaviť jazyk, v ktorom chcete informácie hľadať, pomocou "
"combo boxu <guilabel>Nastavenie jazyka</guilabel>."

